[
  {
    "start": 0.12,
    "end": 1.86,
    "text": "Most portfolios hand you a list."
  },
  {
    "start": 2.56,
    "end": 3.88,
    "text": "Here is where I went to school."
  },
  {
    "start": 4.66,
    "end": 5.66,
    "text": "Here is where I worked."
  },
  {
    "start": 6.4,
    "end": 8.14,
    "text": "Here are some skills I claim to have."
  },
  {
    "start": 9.02,
    "end": 10.28,
    "text": "This one is different."
  },
  {
    "start": 11.48,
    "end": 13.6,
    "text": "My name is Estivan Ayramia."
  },
  {
    "start": 14.3,
    "end": 15.22,
    "text": "I am Chaldean,"
  },
  {
    "start": 15.78,
    "end": 16.74,
    "text": "born in Baghdad,"
  },
  {
    "start": 17.18,
    "end": 18.3,
    "text": "raised in El Cajon,"
  },
  {
    "start": 18.82,
    "end": 19.94,
    "text": "built from the ground up."
  },
  {
    "start": 20.82,
    "end": 23.94,
    "text": "My family crossed borders most people only read about."
  },
  {
    "start": 24.68,
    "end": 27.0,
    "text": "That kind of background does not make you fragile."
  },
  {
    "start": 27.4,
    "end": 28.66,
    "text": "It makes you resourceful."
  },
  {
    "start": 29.56,
    "end": 31.26,
    "text": "This site is not a resume."
  },
  {
    "start": 31.78,
    "end": 32.72,
    "text": "It is a system,"
  },
  {
    "start": 33.34,
    "end": 33.92,
    "text": "structure,"
  },
  {
    "start": 34.46,
    "end": 34.86,
    "text": "proof,"
  },
  {
    "start": 35.52,
    "end": 36.72,
    "text": "real work you can check,"
  },
  {
    "start": 37.34,
    "end": 38.7,
    "text": "not a pitch you have to trust."
  },
  {
    "start": 39.58,
    "end": 41.84,
    "text": "Every project here was built to be examined,"
  },
  {
    "start": 42.58,
    "end": 44.06,
    "text": "not admired from a distance,"
  },
  {
    "start": 44.48,
    "end": 46.06,
    "text": "but pulled apart up close."
  },
  {
    "start": 46.74,
    "end": 48.78,
    "text": "There is a carousel that lets you explore"
  },
  {
    "start": 48.86,
    "end": 49.78,
    "text": "at your own pace,"
  },
  {
    "start": 50.46,
    "end": 52.04,
    "text": "a roulette that decides for you."
  },
  {
    "start": 52.8,
    "end": 55.56,
    "text": "Arcade games because work should not be the"
  },
  {
    "start": 55.66,
    "end": 57.48,
    "text": "only thing that is well crafted."
  },
  {
    "start": 58.42,
    "end": 60.48,
    "text": "Even the AI on this site has a name."
  },
  {
    "start": 61.0,
    "end": 63.88,
    "text": "He is called Savonie, and he will answer"
  },
  {
    "start": 63.98,
    "end": 65.26,
    "text": "almost anything about me."
  },
  {
    "start": 65.8,
    "end": 66.26,
    "text": "Try him."
  },
  {
    "start": 67.24,
    "end": 68.32,
    "text": "I care about people,"
  },
  {
    "start": 69.0,
    "end": 71.88,
    "text": "process, and doing the work right."
  },
  {
    "start": 71.96,
    "end": 74.82,
    "text": "You are about to see all of it. Welcome in."
  }
]